channel.title: Need help with JDK-6 file
channel.description: ok.. In the "ULTIMATE SERVER GUIDE" It says i need jdk-6. So i go to download... and.. it says i need to restart my comp for it to be recognized. I download, and it says it's completed.. But theres nothing on my desktop, in a "new folder" or anything. All i ahve is the jdk-6 downloader. So i tryed clicking it again.. it says " Are you sure you want to download this file again" BUT I CAN'T FIND IT ON MY COMP! Please help me! :|

item.title: Need help with JDK-6 file
item.dc:creator: @Vince Vince`
item.description:
@Vince wrote:

You have the downloader, you’ve downloaded the Installation, am I correct?

If so, go to C:\My Downloads and see if it’s there. If so just double click or click it once to install it.
